{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"46ca2fe893","title":"首都红卫兵纠察队（西城分队）宣告成立","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f5a18a6cd1","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"46ca2fe893","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"edb5c9cfe9","type":"title","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队（西城分队）宣告成立","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"485427e37c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"078594c29a","type":"paragraph","text":"人民靠我们去组织。中国的反动分子，靠我们组织起人民去把他打倒。凡是反动的东西，你不打，他就不倒。这也和扫地一样，扫帚不到，灰尘照例不会自己跑掉。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5af106fb3","type":"paragraph","text":"为了捍卫毛泽东思想，为了支持广大红卫兵造资产阶级的反，为了更好地完成党中央毛主席和广大工农兵群众赋予我们的光荣职责，为了把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底，《首都红卫兵纠察队》宣告成立。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"72e67584ff","type":"paragraph","text":"这个决定是八月二十五日，西城区三十一个学校的红卫兵讨论通过的。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"adaabcd138","type":"paragraph","text":"纠察队是红卫兵自己的组织，他的成员是红卫兵的优秀分子，中坚力量。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3dc6438093","type":"paragraph","text":"纠察队是革命的造反队，是无产阶级专政的工具，是中国人民解放军驻京部队的亲密战友。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2170128e10","type":"paragraph","text":"纠察队是毛泽东思想的宣传队。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc2eafaa87","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队的成立是我们全体红卫兵的大喜事，它再一次表明我们的红卫兵是以毛泽东思想为武器的红色革命组织。既是敢想，敢说，敢革命，敢造反的先锋队，又是坚决执行党的政策，勇敢捍卫毛泽东思想的战斗队。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf9e13fe48","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的职责和权力：","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bc5af0a1ca","type":"paragraph","text":"1．努力学习毛泽东思想，忠实执行毛泽东思想，热情宣传毛泽东思想，勇敢捍卫毛泽东思想。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1f1b798c52","type":"paragraph","text":"2．坚决地协助红卫兵的革命造反行动。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1e0128e66","type":"paragraph","text":"3．坚决镇压地、富、反、坏、右和资产阶级孝子贤孙的反革命行动。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d363cccae6","type":"paragraph","text":"4．有权撤销一切不符合毛泽东思想的宣传品和禁令。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e006155448","type":"paragraph","text":"5．有权检查各学校，各机关，各工厂，各单位的红组织。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f14055bfea","type":"paragraph","text":"6．有权扣押假红卫兵和流氓。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fadd635363","type":"paragraph","text":"7．在其他各区纠察队未成立之前，一些重要国家机关和主要街道，暂由西城分队代行保卫职权。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9abce9e9a5","type":"paragraph","text":"此令八月二十六日十时实行。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92ae57aab4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要求广大工农兵群众和各地区公安机关协助我们工作。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"46ca2fe893","publication":{},"article":{}}